class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Analytics and Data\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports analytics and esports data are the key elements of what we focus the most on.  Not only Esports Charts collects and compiles data, but also uses the stats to conduct research of different scale: from small studies to determining global trends of the entire industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Popularity\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                One of our goals is to measure the popularity of esports. On a daily basis we take into account a wide variety of viewership metrics. Each of them provides a different perspective that helps us to see the full picture of the market.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Viewership and Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports audience varies greatly depending on a discipline, tournament or even season. We analyze esports viewership numbers to understand the current state of affairs in the industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Live and Historical Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                We operate with different esports viewership data. In particular, we track both esports live stats and operate historical esports data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Database\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                In addition to esports viewership statistics, we also maintain a more general esports database, which includes variety of data points. You will find information about esports organizations, teams, tournament operators and individual esports players on our site.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Growth and Dynamics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Our website offers esports viewership statistics from 2016 to a present day. Thus, one can easily study esports audience dynamics based on our data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                    \u003C/div>\n Livewire Component wire-end:zyRlTUJzGcqalSaDbq47 -->                \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"col-span-12 mt-6\" id=\"seo_block\">\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Analytics and Data\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports analytics and esports data are the key elements of what we focus the most on.  Not only Esports Charts collects and compiles data, but also uses the stats to conduct research of different scale: from small studies to determining global trends of the entire industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Popularity\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                One of our goals is to measure the popularity of esports. On a daily basis we take into account a wide variety of viewership metrics. Each of them provides a different perspective that helps us to see the full picture of the market.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Viewership and Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports audience varies greatly depending on a discipline, tournament or even season. We analyze esports viewership numbers to understand the current state of affairs in the industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Live and Historical Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                We operate with different esports viewership data. In particular, we track both esports live stats and operate historical esports data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Database\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                In addition to esports viewership statistics, we also maintain a more general esports database, which includes variety of data points. You will find information about esports organizations, teams, tournament operators and individual esports players on our site.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Growth and Dynamics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Our website offers esports viewership statistics from 2016 to a present day. Thus, one can easily study esports audience dynamics based on our data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                    \u003C/div>\n class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Analytics and Data\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports analytics and esports data are the key elements of what we focus the most on.  Not only Esports Charts collects and compiles data, but also uses the stats to conduct research of different scale: from small studies to determining global trends of the entire industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Popularity\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                One of our goals is to measure the popularity of esports. On a daily basis we take into account a wide variety of viewership metrics. Each of them provides a different perspective that helps us to see the full picture of the market.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Viewership and Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports audience varies greatly depending on a discipline, tournament or even season. We analyze esports viewership numbers to understand the current state of affairs in the industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Live and Historical Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                We operate with different esports viewership data. In particular, we track both esports live stats and operate historical esports data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Database\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                In addition to esports viewership statistics, we also maintain a more general esports database, which includes variety of data points. You will find information about esports organizations, teams, tournament operators and individual esports players on our site.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Growth and Dynamics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Our website offers esports viewership statistics from 2016 to a present day. Thus, one can easily study esports audience dynamics based on our data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                    \u003C/div>\n class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Analytics and Data\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports analytics and esports data are the key elements of what we focus the most on.  Not only Esports Charts collects and compiles data, but also uses the stats to conduct research of different scale: from small studies to determining global trends of the entire industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Popularity\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                One of our goals is to measure the popularity of esports. On a daily basis we take into account a wide variety of viewership metrics. Each of them provides a different perspective that helps us to see the full picture of the market.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Viewership and Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports audience varies greatly depending on a discipline, tournament or even season. We analyze esports viewership numbers to understand the current state of affairs in the industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Live and Historical Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                We operate with different esports viewership data. In particular, we track both esports live stats and operate historical esports data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Database\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                In addition to esports viewership statistics, we also maintain a more general esports database, which includes variety of data points. You will find information about esports organizations, teams, tournament operators and individual esports players on our site.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Growth and Dynamics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Our website offers esports viewership statistics from 2016 to a present day. Thus, one can easily study esports audience dynamics based on our data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                    \u003C/div>\n class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Analytics and Data\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports analytics and esports data are the key elements of what we focus the most on.  Not only Esports Charts collects and compiles data, but also uses the stats to conduct research of different scale: from small studies to determining global trends of the entire industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Popularity\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                One of our goals is to measure the popularity of esports. On a daily basis we take into account a wide variety of viewership metrics. Each of them provides a different perspective that helps us to see the full picture of the market.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Viewership and Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Esports audience varies greatly depending on a discipline, tournament or even season. We analyze esports viewership numbers to understand the current state of affairs in the industry.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Live and Historical Statistics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                We operate with different esports viewership data. In particular, we track both esports live stats and operate historical esports data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Database\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                In addition to esports viewership statistics, we also maintain a more general esports database, which includes variety of data points. You will find information about esports organizations, teams, tournament operators and individual esports players on our site.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-3 border-t border-card\">\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"text-sm font-bold text-secondary\">\n                                Esports Growth and Dynamics\n                            \u003C/div>\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\"pt-2 pb-3 text-xs text-opacity-75 text-secondary\">\n                                Our website offers esports viewership statistics from 2016 to a present day. Thus, one can easily study esports audience dynamics based on our data.\n                            \u003C/div>\n                        \u003C/div>\n                                    \u003C/div>\n
